{"tid":1841472,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]渣打馬拉松宣布取消","createTime":"2020-01-25T09:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T10:43:33.000Z","uid":59283,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"888928fae0f85ef324bc87b1d583da600c946718","tid":1841472,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:27:32.000Z","msg":"【#渣馬2020 宣布取消】<br />\n公眾健康係我哋嘅首要考慮，大會為全面配合政府嘅防疫工作，決定取消原訂於2月8及9日舉行嘅渣打香港馬拉松，並全數退回報名費，詳情將於稍後公布。<br />\n<br />\n【#SCHKM2020 Cancellation Announcement 】<br />\nPublic health is our top priority. To support the government&rsquo;s epidemic prevention efforts, the organiser has decided to cancel the Standard Chartered Hong Kong Marathon originally scheduled for 8 and 9 February. Entry fee will be fully refunded with details to be announced shortly."},{"pid":"375bdcdd94a9d808b7caadd2158de655aae1ed39","tid":1841472,"uid":8500,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"打卡撚末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1200fbb67a45e2a7b90d575fe2e94f0f6d3884c2","tid":1841472,"uid":74171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:30:01.000Z","msg":"一開始以為係反送中攬炒馬拉松，結果係武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d22941718384f8b71a0693cdd8f978f1f8dae70","tid":1841472,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1200fbb67a45e2a7b90d575fe2e94f0f6d3884c2","tid":1841472,"uid":74171,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:30:01.000Z","msg":"一開始以為係反送中攬炒馬拉松，結果係武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"多謝共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edc2f1577c3e2ab74a39de87c928e7e4e21e900","tid":1841472,"uid":26672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1200fbb67a45e2a7b90d575fe2e94f0f6d3884c2","tid":1841472,"uid":74171,"like":8,"dislike